import React from 'react'
import { Outlet } from 'react-router-dom'
import MainNavigation from '../MainNavigation'
import classes from './RootLayout.module.css'

const RootLayout = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <MainNavigation />
      <main className={classes.content}>
        <Outlet />
      </main>
    </>
  )
}

export default RootLayout
